FARM STACK COURSE to build a running app from head to toe

FASTAPI
REACT
MongoDB


https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OzUzrs8uJl8&ab_channel=freeCodeCamp.org - video tutorial

MongoDB community server download https://www.mongodb.com/try/download/community-kubernetes-operator
MongoDB shell - in the msi installation option
CTRL + SHIFT + P to create an environment



Command for starting the code

pip install pipenv
pipenv shell
pipenv install -r requirements.txt


FASTAPI

    Get  / - read root
    GET  /api/todo - Get Todo
    POST /api/todo - Post Todo
    GET  /api/todo{id} - Get Todo by Id
    PUT  /api/todo{id} - Put Todo
  DELETE /api/todo{id} - Delete Todo


  For activating backend

  uvicorn main:app --reload

 For activating backend

npm start
